                        <p>Complete projects, earn certificates, showcase your skills</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 4rem;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">What Makes Octal Foundry Different?</h3>
                <div class="problem-grid">
                    <div class="problem-card">
                        <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">üéØ Personalized to YOU</h4>
                        <p>Not generic tutorials. AI analyzes YOUR specific courses and creates a roadmap that
                            complements what you're learning in class.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="problem-card">
                        <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">‚úÖ Verified Content</h4>
                        <p>Curated videos from trusted channels like freeCodeCamp, 3Blue1Brown, and industry experts‚Äîno
                            random YouTube rabbit holes.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="problem-card">
                        <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">üíº Career-Aligned</h4>
                        <p>Every task builds toward real job requirements. Software Engineer, Data Scientist, DevOps‚Äîwe
                            map to actual job postings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision Section -->
    <section id="vision" class="vision-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-label" style="color: var(--accent);">The Vision</div>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="color: white;">
